com.dryver.Controllers

Class UserController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dryver.Controllers.UserController

  • public class UserController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller for the Current user, as well as the user currently being viewed. Follows the Singleton design pattern, allows user to view ActivityEditProfile.
